name: #4 WRATH
description: As ruler of the dark Valley of the Vile, Wrath reigned over the wretched and depraved. Hunting humans as prey, adding to his army of slaves. When hunters charged the Valley in vengeance they were ravaged in a blood bath. With the survivors turned into examples, for whoever shall ever walk the Wrath's territory unknown shall be skinned yet torn to shreds. The Valley of the Vile still echoes with the cries of our lost hunters.
